<div class="furadoption-content-wrapper">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1 class="about-title">Fur Adoption</h1>
    </div>


<main class="furadoption-main">
     
  <section class="adoption-process-card">
    <h2 class="adoption-process-title">Adoption Process</h2>
    <p class="adoption-process-desc">Interested in giving a cat their fur-ever home?<br>
    Kindly <strong>book an interview</strong> with our team. One of our PUSA admins will review your application to ensure each cat goes to a safe and loving environment.</p>
    <div class="adoption-process-note">
      <img src="/img/info.png" alt="Info" class="adoption-process-icon" />
      <em>Note: Interviews are required before any adoption can proceed.</em>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="adoption-cat-cards-group">
    <img src="/img/b2.png" alt="Nightowl badge" class="adoption-cat-b2" />
    <img src="/img/b4.png" alt="b4" class="adoption-cat-b4" />
    <section class="adoption-cat-card">
      <img src="/img/c1.png" alt="Dweety" class="adoption-cat-img" />
      <div class="adoption-cat-content">
        <div class="adoption-cat-name-row">
          <h3 class="adoption-cat-name">Nightowl</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="adoption-cat-desc">A campus favorite with a charming smile, Nightowl became an instant hit online. Calm, sweet, and friendly, he's adored by many Lasallians. Will you be the lucky one to give this social media star his own loving fur-ever home?</p>
        <button class="adoption-cat-btn">Book Adoption Interview</button>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="adoption-cat-card">
      <img src="/img/c2.png" alt="Mochi" class="adoption-cat-img" />
      <div class="adoption-cat-content">
        <h3 class="adoption-cat-name">Dweety</h3>
        <p class="adoption-cat-desc">Sassy and confident, Dweety struts through campus like a queen. Her stunning fur and bold attitude have won hearts across students and staff. She's looking for someone worthy of her trust â€” are you her fur-ever match?</p>
        <button class="adoption-cat-btn">Book Adoption Interview</button>
      </div>
    </section>
    <img src="/img/b3.png" alt="Nightowl badge" class="adoption-cat-b3" />
    <img src="/img/b5.png" alt="Nightowl badge" class="adoption-cat-b5" />
    <section class="adoption-cat-card">
      <img src="/img/c3.png" alt="Tiger" class="adoption-cat-img" />
      <div class="adoption-cat-content">
        <h3 class="adoption-cat-name">Jackpot</h3>
        <p class="adoption-cat-desc">Friendly and outgoing, Jackpot is a bright orange boy often seen near Vito Cruz. Loved by passersby, he's ready to trade city streets for a cozy home. Will you be the one to give this sweet explorer a fresh start?</p>
        <button class="adoption-cat-btn">Book Adoption Interview</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>
</div>
